name: Jamie Rizzful
id: And yes, that's me in the picture
bio: I'm a Millenial. It's not my fault that my last name has happened to be the buzzword of GenZ. However, it does truly fit me. I've mastered the art of ‘rizz’.  So, any ladies… if you want to join my company, you'll be blown away. And you won't regret it…
